[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectory-entry size, offset fields, multiplication overflow, and ensuring `doff + [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ms ≤ size`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and switched some parameters to `size_t`. After reapplying the patch, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe same overflow still occurs at the updated location in [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry`, indicating the added guards did not prevent the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mout-of-bounds read.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fuzzer Command  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  `[0m[35m/out/[0m[95mexif_from_data_fuzzer[0m[39m -[0m[33mrss_limit_mb[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m2560[0m[39m -[0m[33mtimeout[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m25[0m[39m -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m`[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Crash Summary  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  AddressSanitizer reports a heap-buffer-overflow in `exif_data_load_data_entry`:[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  READ of size [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m at [0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  #[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m  __asan_memcpy … asan_interceptors_memintrinsics.cpp:[0m[1;36m63[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  #[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m  exif_data_load_data_entry … exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:213[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Memory Region  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  The overflow read starts at byte [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m of a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte heap allocation, then reads [0m[1;36m16[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes beyond.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Key Observations in Initial Log[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The directory entry header is assumed to occupy [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m bytes, but there is no check [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mensuring `offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m ≤ size`.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The code computes `s = format_size * components` and determines `doff` based on [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`. Neither branch fully bounds-checks `doff + s` against the input buffer [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize before `memcpy`.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The crash stack trace:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  exif_data_load_data_entry[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  exif_data_load_data_content[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  exif_data_load_data[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  exif_data_new_from_data[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[33m...[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The allocation for `entry->data` matches `s`, yet the copy reads bytes beyond [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat allocation.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch rewrote `exif_data_load_data_entry` to:[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Change parameters from `unsigned int size, offset` to `size_t size, offset`.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Check that the [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte directory entry header fits:  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Read `tag`, `format`, `components`.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Compute `unit_size = [0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `comp = components`. Abort [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif `unit_size == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`, `comp == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`, or `unit_size * comp` overflows `SIZE_MAX`.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   `s = unit_size * comp;`[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Check that the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte “value or offset” field is in bounds:  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Choose `doff` = either the embedded data offset or `offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m`.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Check that `doff + s ≤ size` before copy.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff + s > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. Allocate `entry->data` of length `s`, then `[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Patched Function Context[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```diff[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--- a/libexif/exif-data.c[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+++ b/libexif/exif-data.c[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m@@ [0m[1;36m-162[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m7[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m162[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m7[0m[39m @@ static int [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data,[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-   [0m[1;39m([0m[39mold signature[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+   [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew signature: size_t size, size_t offset[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Ensure directory entry [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m12[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m fits in buffer *[0m[35m/[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     entry->tag        = [0m[1;35mexif_get_short[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     entry->format     = [0m[1;35mexif_get_short[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     entry->components = exif_get_long [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m@@ [0m[1;36m-184[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m184[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m @@ static int [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     unit_size = [0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     comp      = entry->components;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Check multiplication overflow and zero sizes *[0m[35m/[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39munit_size == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || comp == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || unit_size > SIZE_MAX [0m[35m/[0m[39m comp[0m[1;39m)[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    s = unit_size * comp;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Ensure offset field is in buffer *[0m[35m/[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         doff = [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     else[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m@@ [0m[1;36m-192[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m202[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m @@ static int [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Ensure data fits in buffer *[0m[35m/[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff + s > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     entry->data = [0m[1;35mexif_data_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!entry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     entry->size = s;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Copy entry data *[0m[35m/[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Log After Applying Patch[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer was rerun with the same arguments.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The crash now occurs at a slightly different line in the same function:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  AddressSanitizer: heap-buffer-overflow … exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:222[0m[39m in [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  READ of size [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m at [0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack trace structure and allocation size remain the same, indicating the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mboundary checks did not prevent the out-of-bounds copy.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas for Further Investigation[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Offset Calculation Logic**: The conditions distinguishing small [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s ≤ [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m vs. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlarge data blocks and the computation of `doff` may allow a branch that bypasses [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe `doff + s` check.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Component and Format Sizes**: Verify that `exif_format_get_size` and [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`components` values cannot produce misleading `s` values or wrapped offsets.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Caller Context**: Examine how `size` and `offset` are determined in [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_content` and `exif_data_load_data` to ensure entries are [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsed with the correct bounds.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Buffer Construction**: Review how the input buffer `d` is formed and passed in [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom the fuzzer harness to ensure `size` truly represents available data.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Related Functions**: Check neighboring functions [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_content`, `exif_data_new_from_data`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for missing or [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minconsistent size validations.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m965[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_CORRUPT_DATA,[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m966[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, [0m[1;35m_[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unknown encoding."[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m967[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m968[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m969[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m970[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Fixed value *[0m[35m/[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m971[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m != [0m[1;36m0x002a[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m972[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m973[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m974[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* IFD [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m offset *[0m[35m/[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m975[0m[39m:    [0m[39moffset = exif_get_long [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m976[0m[39m:    [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m977[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"IFD 0 at %i."[0m[39m, [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m978[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m979[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* ds is restricted to [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bit above, so offset is restricted too, and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffset+[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m should not overflow. *[0m[35m/[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m980[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > ds || offset + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m > ds[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m981[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m982[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m983[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Parse the actual exif data [0m[1;39m([0m[39musually offset [0m[1;36m14[0m[39m from start[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:168[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m176[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m168[0m[39m:    [0m[39munsigned int s, doff;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m169[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m170[0m[39m:    [0m[39mentry->tag        = exif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m171[0m[39m:    [0m[39mentry->format     = exif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m172[0m[39m:    [0m[39mentry->components = exif_get_long  [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m173[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m174[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* FIXME: should use exif_tag_get_name_in_ifd here but entry->parent [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m175[0m[39m:    [0m[39m * has not been set yet[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m176[0m[39m:    [0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Strengthen and unify all offset-and-size boundary checks in [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` by using overflow-safe idioms [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor the existing [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CHECKOVERFLOW` macro[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m instead of raw additions. This prevents wrap-around and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mguarantees that every memory access stays within bounds:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Replace[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        “if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;”[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      with[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        “if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, size, [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;”[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      or equivalently[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        “if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > size ‑ [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;”[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Replace[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        “if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;”[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      with[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        “if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, size, [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;”[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      or[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        “if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m > size ‑ [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;”[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Replace[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        “if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff + s > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;”[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      with[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        “if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, size, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;”[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      or[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        “if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff > size ‑ s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;”[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This eliminates any arithmetic overflow in the checks themselves and enforces [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat header, offset-field, and data-copy windows all lie fully inside the input [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add an explicit sanity check on the fetched data offset for large entries [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhere[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m && doff < offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This ensures that when the format indicates out-of-line data, the offset read [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom the file cannot point back inside the [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte directory header or otherwise [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstray into metadata space.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Audit the caller in `exif_data_load_data_content` to bound the per-entry header [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore invoking the entry loader:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Compute `entry_offset = base_offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m*i` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter reading the [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcount[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Before calling `[0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[39md, ds, entry_offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, do:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry_offset, ds, [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m continue;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This prevents corrupted “count” values or large `i` loops from overflowing the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mper-entry header calculation.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptional but recommended[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In `exif_data_load_data`, remove or adjust the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtruncation `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mds > [0m[1;36m0xFFFE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ds = [0m[1;36m0xFFFE[0m[39m;`. Instead, keep `ds` equal to the actual [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minput size [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor at least propagate it as a safe [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m- or [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m-bit value[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and rely on the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnew per-entry `CHECKOVERFLOW` steps to prevent wraps. Eliminating arbitrary [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m KiB [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcapping both preserves real bounds for fuzzing and avoids mismatches between real [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer length and clamped `ds`.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Maintain the existing logic around small values [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s ≤ [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m—inline copying from [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe directory entry—as long as the header and offset-field checks [0m[1;39m([0m[39mabove[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m pass. [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThat preserves all current functional behavior [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., inline values vs. [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffset-based values, MakerNote logging[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Using `CHECKOVERFLOW` ensures that any addition like `offset + N` or `doff + s` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcannot wrap around the size word and slip past the guard.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– An extra check `doff ≥ offset+[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m` for out-of-line data prevents nonsensical [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m“offset” values from pointing into or before the directory header.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Guarding in the content loader that each [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte directory entry lies entirely in[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe buffer adds a missing layer of defense and stops malformed “count” fields from [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindexing junk.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Removing the [0m[1;36m0xFFFE[0m[39m clamp [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor at least not using it as the sole source of truth [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor `size`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ensures boundary checks reflect the true input length and not an [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39martificial cap.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– This strategy does not touch fuzzing harness code, does not suppress errors [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mglobally, does not catch overly broad exceptions, and preserves all existing [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding the small-data optimization and MakerNote behavior[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPotential Side Effects and Mitigations:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Removing the [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m KiB clamp may slightly increase the parsing surface for huge [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs; however, the new per-entry and arithmetic-overflow checks fully protect [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39magainst any out-of-bounds reads.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– The slight performance cost of extra `CHECKOVERFLOW` calls is minimal compared to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe critical safety guarantees required for fuzzing.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Tests and existing code paths remain unchanged except for the hardened guards, so[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbackwards compatibility and test suites should pass without alteration.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReferences:[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– The `CHECKOVERFLOW` macro is already defined at the top of `exif-data.c`.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– The same pattern is used elsewhere in the codebase [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., protecting the [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m-byte [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte reads for IFD offsets[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– By mirroring that approach here, we maintain style consistency and correctness.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m[12/28/25 13:34:35][0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.ANALYZE                  ]8;id=742066;file:///home/user/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=649359;file:///home/user/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\

[2;36m                    [0m         -       entry->tag        = exif_get_short [1m([0md + offset + [1;36m0[0m, data->priv->order[1m)[0m;     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                          size_t size, size_t offset[1m)[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +[1m{[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       uint64_t total;                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       size_t doff;                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       unsigned int unit_size, comp, s;                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       [35m/[0m* Ensure header and offset fields fit in buffer [1m([0m[1;36m12[0m bytes total[1m)[0m *[35m/[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       if [1m([0moffset > size - [1;36m12[0m[1m)[0m [1m{[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +               exif_log [1m([0mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [32m"ExifData"[0m,         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                         [32m"Entry header past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu > %zu[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m, offset,    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         size[1m)[0m;                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +               return [1;36m0[0m;                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       [1m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       [35m/[0m* Read entry header *[35m/[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       entry->tag        = exif_get_short [1m([0md + offset, data->priv->order[1m)[0m;         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                 entry->format     = exif_get_short [1m([0md + offset + [1;36m2[0m, data->priv->order[1m)[0m;     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                 entry->components = exif_get_long  [1m([0md + offset + [1;36m4[0m, data->priv->order[1m)[0m;     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       [35m/[0m* FIXME: should use exif_tag_get_name_in_ifd here but entry->parent        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -        * has not been set yet                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -        *[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                 exif_log [1m([0mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [32m"ExifData"[0m,                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                           [32m"Loading entry 0x%x [0m[32m([0m[32m'%s'[0m[32m)[0m[32m..."[0m, entry->tag,                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                           exif_tag_get_name [1m([0mentry->tag[1m)[0m[1m)[0m;                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       [35m/[0m* [1m{[0m[1;36m0[0m,[1;36m1[0m,[1;36m2[0m,[1;36m4[0m,[1;36m8[0m[1m}[0m x [1m{[0m [1;36m0x00000000[0m .. [1;36m0xffffffff[0m [1m}[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -        *   -> [1m{[0m [1;36m0x000000000[0m .. [1;36m0x7fffffff8[0m [1m}[0m *[35m/[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       s = [1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1m([0mentry->format[1m)[0m * entry->components;                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       if [1m([0m[1m([0ms [1m<[0m[39m entry->components[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Compute total data size safely *[0m[35m/[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[39munit_size = exif_format_get_size [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[39mcomp      = entry->components;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39munit_size == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || comp == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-       [0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-       [0m[39m * Size? If bigger than [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes, the actual data is not[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-       [0m[39m * in the entry but somewhere else [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-       [0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotal > SIZE_MAX || total > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmpnctwfke5[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexif_from_data_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer‐detected heap‐buffer‐overflow occurs in [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` when a fuzzer input causes `memcpy` to read past the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mend of the allocated buffer. The attempted patch changes the function to use [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`size_t` parameters, adds `CHECKOVERFLOW` checks for header fields and the data [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mblock, and guards the directory‐entry loop. Despite these additions, the same [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow is still reported at the `memcpy` call in `exif_data_load_data_entry`, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating the bounds checks did not prevent the out‐of‐bounds read.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - During fuzzing of `exif_from_data_fuzzer`, AddressSanitizer reports a [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap‐buffer‐overflow at  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     `exif_data_load_data_entry` → `[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow reads [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes at the very end of a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m‐byte region, implying [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`doff + s` exceeds the allocated buffer length.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Call stack highlights the path: `exif_data_new_from_data` → [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data` → `exif_data_load_data_content` → [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry`.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key observations in the initial log  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The allocated region is [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0x511000000180[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow occurs exactly at offset [0m[1;36m0x24f[0m[39m, i.e., [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m bytes past the end, on a [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m16[0m[39m‐byte read.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No checks in the original code ensure that `doff + s` stays within the input [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Changed `exif_data_load_data_entry` signature to accept `size_t size, size_t [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffset`.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduced boundary checks using a `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbase, limit, length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` macro [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore:  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Reading the [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m‐byte directory entry header [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Reading the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m‐byte data‐offset field [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Copying the data block [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`doff + s`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added a check to reject out‐of‐line data that points inside the header region.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the IFD parsing loop, added a `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m*i, ds, [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` guard [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore calling the entry loader.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Post‐patch results  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer still triggers an AddressSanitizer heap‐buffer‐overflow at [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry:[0m[1;36m231[0m[39m`, the `memcpy` line.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The error location, read size [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and allocation region remain [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39midentical to the pre‐patch failure.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This indicates that either `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, size, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` did not catch the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvalid range or the parameters [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`size`, `offset`, `ds`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m were not as expected.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Areas for further investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify the definition and behavior of `CHECKOVERFLOW` to ensure it correctly [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mflags all out‐of‐bounds scenarios.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that the `size` parameter passed to `exif_data_load_data_entry` always[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatches the actual buffer length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ds`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in all call sites.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Examine how `exif_data_load_data_content` computes and passes `ds` and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`offset` into the entry loader.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Inspect `[0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `entry->components` for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpotential multiplication overflow or zero‐size formats.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Review `exif_data_alloc` to ensure the requested allocation size [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m aligns [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith expectations and that failure paths do not leave uninitialized pointers.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Check inline‐data handling when `s <= [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`, since `doff` is set to `offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand may bypass certain checks.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
