[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m326[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       unsigned int ds, ExifLong o, ExifLong s[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m327[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m328[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Sanity checks *[0m[35m/[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m329[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mo >= ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m330[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"Bogus [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mthumbnail offset [0m[32m([0m[32m%u[0m[32m)[0m[32m."[0m[39m, o[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m331[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m332[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m333[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mo,ds,s[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m334[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"Bogus [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mthumbnail size [0m[32m([0m[32m%u[0m[32m)[0m[32m, max would be %u."[0m[39m, s, ds-o[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-format.[0m[1;92mc:65[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m74[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m65[0m[39m:unsigned char[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m66:e[0m[39mxif_format_get_size [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifFormat format[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m67[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m68[0m[39m:     [0m[39munsigned int i;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m69[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m70[0m[39m:     [0m[39mfor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; ExifFormatTable[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.size; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m71[0m[39m:     [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifFormatTable[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.format == format[0m[1;39m)[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m72[0m[39m:     [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn ExifFormatTable[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.size;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m73[0m[39m:     [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m74[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:531[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m533[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m531[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexif_data_load_data_entry [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, entry, d, ds,[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m532[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m   offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * i[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m533[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_content_add_entry [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->ifd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mifd[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, entry[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The root cause is a silent [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit integer overflow when computing `s = [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * components` and a gaps-in-manual-checks pattern [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`doff >= size` and `s > size - doff`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that can be bypassed if `size - doff` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munderflows. Although the attempted patch uses `CHECKOVERFLOW`, its semantics [0m[1;39m([0m[39mas [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mused elsewhere[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m only catch `s > datasize - offset`, not all unwanted wrap or [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmultiplication-overflow cases. We will therefore:  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Add an explicit [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m-bit multiplication and clamp so that any product exceeding[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UINT_MAX` or the buffer length is rejected.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Replace/augment `CHECKOVERFLOW` reliance with concise manual checks that [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mforbid `offset + header_bytes` from exceeding `datasize`, [0m[1;39m([0m[39mii[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m verify `s` does not [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexceed the entire buffer, and [0m[1;39m([0m[39miii[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ensure `doff + s` fits safely within [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`datasize`.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Mirror the proven thumbnail-loader pattern for consistency.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Detailed Steps in exif_data_load_data_entry  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Enforce header-field safety before reading tag/format/components:[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Insert  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > size - [0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      This guarantees `d + offset + [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m..[0m[1;36m7[0m[39m` lies within the buffer.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Read `entry->tag`, `entry->format`, `entry->components` as before.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Compute the unit size and total byte count in [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m bits:[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `unsigned unit_size = [0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `unsigned comp = entry->components;`  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - If `unit_size == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || comp == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`, return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Compute `uint64_t total = [0m[1;39m([0m[39muint64_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39munit_size * comp;`  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - If `total > UINT_MAX` or `total > size`, return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Cast `unsigned s = [0m[1;39m([0m[39munsigned[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m total;`[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Determine `doff` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - If `s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         - Ensure reading the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte offset field is safe:  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > size - [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         - `doff = [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Else [0m[1;39m([0m[39minline data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         - `doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;`[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Bounds-check the block at `d + doff` of length `s`:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - If `doff > size - s`, return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      This single test covers both `doff >= size` and `s > size - doff`, preventing[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39many unsigned underflow gap.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   f[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Allocate and copy:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `entry->data = [0m[1;35mexif_data_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - If allocation fails, log and return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `entry->size = s;`  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   g[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m MakerNote handling remains unchanged.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. IFD-loop guard in exif_data_load_data_content  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The patch’s addition  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m*i, ds, [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m break;  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   correctly ensures each directory entry header [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m12[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lies within the buffer.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWe retain this. Since the entry loader now has its own header-check, the loop-guard[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis redundant but harmless.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Why This Works  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m-bit multiplication check prevents wraparound of large component counts [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor formats.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `offset > size - X` idiom and `doff > size - s` are classical safe-bounds [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtests that do not rely on macros whose semantics might vary.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We mirror the thumbnail loader’s approach [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexplicit checks then memcpy[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mensure consistency across the codebase.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All existing functionality [0m[1;39m([0m[39minline data, out-of-line data, MakerNote, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mzero-length or oversized entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is preserved or cleanly rejected, rather than [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtruncated or undefined.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side Effects and Mitigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Some extreme, non-conformant EXIF files that previously produced huge `s` via [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwraparound will now be rejected rather than mis-parsed; this is safer and in line [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith the library’s defensive posture.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance cost is negligible: one [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m-bit multiply, two branch checks.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes to fuzzer harness, no external dependencies are touched.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References in Codebase  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Thumbnail loader [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_data_load_data_thumbnail`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m uses the same pattern: an [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mearly `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mo >= ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mo, ds, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return;`, `[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The multiplication-overflow concept is analogous to other places where [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`unit_size * comp` could overflow, but here is the critical security boundary.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Summary of Patch Locations  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Modify `exif_data_load_data_entry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround lines [0m[1;36m163[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m231[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to implement the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mabove checks.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Retain the IFD-entry loop guard in `exif_data_load_data_content` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround lines[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m528[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m540[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No other files or harness logic are modified.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure tests and fuzzer harness remain unchanged and passing.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
